<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>zài qù xún qǐ chū de xīn 迦南37</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 nǐ de xīn wèi hé zhè yàng yōu mèn? nǐ de líng wèi hé zhè yàng kū gān?
 nǐ kàn bāng zhù nǐ de shì shéi, nǐ tīng zhǔ shuō huà de shēng yīn;
 qǐ chū de ài xīn hé chù qù? qǐ chū de bēn pǎo zài nǎ lǐ?
 qǐ chū de xīn yuàn yǐ bèi zhǔ jì niàn, xiàn zài nǐ wèi hé méi yǒu yǔ yán?
 chāi huǐ nǐ xīn zhōng de qiáng, zài qù xún nǐ qǐ chū de xīn.
 zhǔ de xīn duō jiāo jí, zhǔ de yǎn wàng zhe wǒ hé nǐ.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>37</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>